; Test account directive assert/check (lines 445-465 of textual_directives.cc)
; Exercise the assert and check sub-directives within account directive

account Expenses:Food
    assert amount > 0
    check  amount < $1000.00

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
